programme.title: Bidadari: Derhaka Cinta Jebat Ep22
programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. Bijaknya Jebat mengatur rancangan agar Aisyah jatuh cinta padanya hingga membawa kepada sebuah perkahwinan dengan niat ingin membalas dendam. Aisyah Humaira, suatu ketika dahulu pernah menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan adik lelaki Jebat, iaitu Tuah Iskandar. Tanpa usul periksa Jebat menjatuhkan hukuman tanpa memberi peluang kepada Aisyah untuk menjelaskan segala-galanya. Aisyah dituduh berlaku curang dengan Tuah dan menjadi penyebab musibah yang menimpa adik lelaki kesayangannya. Aisyah benar-benar kecewa. Jebat mendustai cintanya. Dia dinikahi Jebat bukan untuk disayang, dicintai sepenuh hati tapi Jebat punya agendanya sendiri. Misi Jebat hanyalah satu, melunaskan dendamnya dan membalas balik segala kesengsaraan Tuah yang kononnya dikhianati Aisyah dahulu.

programme.title: Ustaz Adik Cik
programme.desc: Elisa yang perlu menjaga dua anak saudaranya, Arif, 16 thn, dan Afik, 8 thn, ketika ibu bapa mereka pergi ke Mekah untuk tunaikan haji. Elisa yang selama ini berlagak baik di hadapan keluarga tapi sebenarnya seorang yang gemar bersosial, terpaksa menyesuaikan diri ketika menjaga Arif dan Afik. Sikap Arif yang suka bermain dan malas belajar, membuatkan Arif lebih rapat dan suka pada Elisa. Tetapi lain pula Afik yang lebih alim dan baik, sering persoalkan tindakan Elisa yang suka benarkan Arif bawa kawan-kawan datang ke rumah bermain sehingga abaikan solat dan kerja sekolah. Berbuih mulut Afik menasihati Arif dan Elisa tetapi mereka degil dan tetap malas hendak solat. Kerana tidak tahan melihat kemungkaran yang berlaku dalam rumah, Afik keluar untuk tenangkan jiwanya di masjid. Tetapi ketika itulah dia diculik oleh sekumpulan penjenayah dan ini membuat Arif dan Elisa rasa amat bersalah.

programme.title: Kaki Bahan S5 Ep03
programme.desc: Kaki Bahan merupakan sebuah rancangan komedi yang akan berkongsikan video-video popular lagi lucu dengan caranya tersendiri.

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1 Ep21
programme.desc: Aris yang bekerja dia Miri, bercadang untuk menghabiskan cuti bersama teman baiknya, Fahad menikmati keindahan alam semulajadi di Hutan Simpan Mulu Sarawak. Sementara itu, Jihan dan Maria yang baru selesai mendaki Gunung Santubong, bercadang untuk melanjutkan percutian mereka ke Mulu sebelum pulang ke Kuala Lumpur. Mereka berempat mula bertemu sewaktu berada di Mulu. Pertemuan pertama kali membuatkan Aris jatuh cinta dengan Maria, dan dalam masa yang sama, menyedari yang Fahad juga menyukai Maria. Malangnya, Jihan dar awal memang tida menyukai dua orang lelaki yang baginya hanya menyusahkan itu. Sepanjang ekspedisi mereka, Jihan yang sentiasa berperanan sebagai seorang kakak nampak kurang senang apabila Maria kerap melayan Aris dan Fahad. Sedikit situasi berlaku di dalam Gua Mulu mengakibatkan Jihan tercedera dan tidak dapat ikut serta pada ekspedisi mereka keesokan hari. Disebabkan terlalu geram dan menyalahkan Fahad atas apa yang berlaku, Fahad juga ditahan dari ikut serta ekspedisi yang akan dijalankan. Akhrinya, hanya Maria dan Aris bersama beberapa orang pengunjung lain yang menyertai ekspedisi tersebut. Di dalam hutan, kerana terlalu teruja dan leka, Maria tersesat dan terpisah dari orang lain. Nasibnya baik kerana Aris ada untuk menyelamatkannya, tetapi mereka akhirnya dapati yang mereka berdua telah sama sama sesat di dalan hutan itu. Aris melindungi Maria sepanjang masa mereka di dalam hutan itu sehingga hari gelap. Dan tiba tiba pada malam hari, mereka diserang dan Aris disumpit.

programme.title: Who Are You Ep09
programme.desc: Buku nota Meen dijumpai dalam beg Tida dalam satu kejadian di kelas 5/3. Meen tanya Tida adakah sekarang dia tahu apa rasanya bila dibuli dan bila tiada siapa percayakan dia.

programme.title: The Gadis Ep04
programme.desc: Memperkenalkan watak utama dalam drama ini. Mengisahkan dua gadis remaja Alina dan adiknya Alisa. Mereka tinggal dengan bapanya yang mengalami lumpuh, ibu mereka telah meninggal dunia. Alina terpaksa berhenti sekolah walaupun mendapat kelulusan cemerlang dalam peperiksaan SPM. Beliau terpaksa bekerja mencuci dan membersih rumah penduduk, termasuk rumah Nek Timah dan Imah bagi menampung keperluan keluarga. Alina tidak mahu Alisa berhenti sekolah sepertinya. Alisa pelajar cemerlang, sedang bersaing dengan Mei Fen menjadi pelajar cemerlang bagi mendapat hadiah RM20 ribu. Satu hari, Lina pergi menjenguk Nek TImah dan bertembung dengan kekasih lamanya, Shazman anak kepada Imah yang kini berjaya menghabiskan pelajaran di kolej. Lina ditegur Nad, kawan lama sekolah Lina dan juga cucu kepada Nek Timah ketika berada di rumah Nek Timah. Lina terpaku dengan kecantikan dan kekayaan Nad. Lina ternampak mesej dari Mika di telefon Nad dan mula ragu-ragu dengan pekerjaannya. Nad pula mulai berbaik dengan Lisa kerana dia mempunyai agenda tersendiri bagi memerangkap Lisa bekerja sepertinya sebagai Sugar Baby.

programme.title: Japanizi Going Going Gong Ep15
programme.desc: Japanizi Going Going Gong ialah pertunjukan permainan fizikal kanak-kanak Kanada dengan motif Jepun di mana peserta bersaing dengan rakan sepasukan menentang pasukan lain semasa mereka menangani halangan dan cabaran untuk menguji keupayaan mental, kekuatan, ketahanan dan kepintaran mereka.

programme.title: #ustazmasak S2 Ep11

Berkonsepkan outdoor cooking, rancangan ini membawakan resepi masakan yang menarik dan enak yang akan dimasak bersama Fendi dan Ustaz jemputan. Rancangan ini bercorak Santai namun tetap menyelitkan informasi berguna seperti petua-petua yang dilupakan.

programme.title: Kembang Kantil
programme.desc: Untuk menghadiri persembahan teater Alisa (Bella Ireland) pergi ke rumah abangnya Anton (Fadika Royandi) dan isterinya Santi (Nafa Urbach). Di rumah Alisa bertemu Tania (Richelle Georgette Skonicki), anak angkat Anton dan Siska.

programme.title: Hitman
programme.desc: Comrade Tanthai(Chatchai Plengpanich) an infamous and highly professional hit man accepts a new assignment from Chaba(Bongkuch Kongmalai),ex-lover of high-ranking mafia honcho, Wong (Thanit Jatanukul). The assignment is to find and kill the drug lord and Godfather of Chinatown, Leemeng(Nirud Sirijanya). Leemeng's death opens up a conflict between the mafia of both the official and unofficial kind. Everyone is now after Tanthai no matter what the cost.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Bertahun-tahun selepas kematian ibunya, seorang wanita yang mengalami kerosakan emosi mencari bapanya yang hilang dan menghadapi masa lalunya.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep 5 Ep5
programme.desc: Kimi dan Tasya ikut Daniel serta Suhana melawat kubur Suzana. Tasya dirasuk semasa perjalanan balik dan menyanyikan lagu Tepukamai-amai tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Hunter Killer
programme.desc: Kapal selam kelas Los Angeles AS USS Tampa Bay hilang ketika membayangi kapal selam kelas Akula Rusia Konek di Artik. Laksamana Muda John Fisk (Common) menghantar kapal selam kelas Virginia USS Arkansas, di bawah perintah Komander Joe Glass (Gerard Butler) yang baru dinaikkan pangkat dan tidak ortodoks untuk menyiasat. Pada masa yang sama, pasukan Navy SEAL di bawah pimpinan Leftenan Bill Beaman dihantar untuk memerhatikan pangkalan tentera laut Rusia secara diam-diam. Apabila mereka tiba di pangkalan tentera laut, mereka menyaksikan menteri pertahanan Dmitri Durov melakukan rampasan kuasa dan menawan Presiden Rusia Zakarin, dan dengan cepat menyedari bahawa Durov berhasrat untuk mencetuskan perang.

programme.title: Paku
programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan tentang Fahmi (Johan As'ari) yang amat mencintai isterinya Riana (Aishah Ilias) dan dia tidak dapat menerima kenyataan bahawa isterinya sudah meninggal dunia. Oleh kerna disebabkan ketaksuban cintanya itu membuatkan Fahmi sanggup mencari seorang bomoh untuk menghidupkan semula Riana. Riana telah berjaya dihidupkan semula dan mereka bersatu sehinggalah Riana melahirkan seorang anak. Namun benarkah itu adalah Riana? Apakah yang akan terjadi kepada kehidupan Fahmi selepas itu?

programme.title: Arjuna Ep22
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: TABU: Mengusik Gerbang Iblis
programme.desc: Mengisahkan sekumpulan 6 orang sahabat muda yang secara tidak sengaja memasuki hutan larangan di Leuweung Hejo. Mereka ialah Diaz, Keyla, Tio , Adis, Muti dan Mahir. Selepas memasuki hutan, mereka menjalankan aktiviti yang dianggap pantang larang.

programme.title: Impetigore @ Perempuan Tanah Jahanam
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang keinginan Maya dalam mengungkap misteri keluarganya. Hal itu bermula ketika Maya mengalami permasalahan termasuk dalam pekerjaannya bersama dengan Dini. Masalah itu membuatnya ingin 'rehat' sejenak dengan mengunjungi tanah leluhurnya.

programme.title: Jodoh Syaitan
programme.desc: Filem ini Mengisahkan tentang Megat, seorang pemuda kampung yang sering menemui kegagalan dalam percintaan dan diminta ibunya untuk pulang ke kampung kerana ingin mengahwinkannya dengan seorang gadis bernama Mawar. Pada masa yang sama, Tok Chai bersama dua pengikut setianya yang juga kawan Megat di kampung iaitu Awang dan Kulup sedang sibuk mencari mayat untuk dipaku, dengan harapan ia hidup semula untuk dijadikan isteri kepada Tok Chai bagi memenuhi hawa nafsunya.

programme.title: Hikayat Merong Mahawangsa
programme.desc: Pada tahun 120,Empayar Romketika itu di bawah pemerintahan Hadrian sementara di negara China,Dinasti Hanmerupakan sebuah empayar yang kuat dan telah memperluaskan pemerintahannya ke negara Asia Tengah. Semasa angkatan Rom sedang membaik pulih kapal mereka diGoa, mereka meminta pertolongan Merong Mahawangsa mengiringi Putera Rom ke Langkasuka (dikatakan terletak di utara Malaysia) untuk berkahwin dengan seorang Puteri China yang cantik dari Dinasti Han.

programme.title: Cicakman 1
programme.desc: Hairi bekerja di Klon Technologies mencari vaksin baharu untuk penyakit baharu.Dia terlalu malu untuk mendekati Tania, gadis yang dicintainya (setiausaha Profesor Klon) dan cukup janggal untuk menelan cicak-cicak yang jatuh dalam cawan kopinya.Cicak itu telah dicemari oleh virus baru dan Hairi telah mendapat beberapa ciri "cicak".Maka, seorang super hero baru lahir: Cicakman.

programme.title: Azem 2
programme.desc: Beberapa orang membawa seorang gadis yang dirasuk teruk dengan kotak kayu berkunci untuk menyembuhkannya.

programme.title: UC 3
programme.desc: Kadir adalah seorang lelaki yang menjadi mangsa ilmu hitam ibunya untuk memisahkannya daripada setiap wanita, termasuk isterinya, yang akan terfikir untuk mendekatinya. Tetapi keadaan menjadi terbalik bertentangan dengan jangkaan ibunya.

programme.title: Siccin 1
programme.desc: znur adalah seorang wanita muda dan cantik. Dia mempunyai cinta platonik sejak kecil kepada Kudret, yang merupakan sepupunya. Kudret bagaimanapun telah berkahwin dengan seorang wanita bernama Nisa dan sangat gembira. Cemburu, znur menggunakan ilmu hitam yang dahsyat untuk mengubahnya supaya dia dan Kudret akan bersama. Walau bagaimanapun, dia tidak bersedia untuk kejahatan yang ditimbulkan oleh mantera ini

programme.title: Taxi 5
programme.desc: Seorang pegawai polis yang ditukarkan dalam polis Marseilles ditugaskan untuk menumpaskan sekumpulan perompak Itali yang memandu Ferrari berkuasa bersama anak saudara Daniel yang lebih tua, seorang pemandu yang teruk yang mendapat teksi putih legenda.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Tom yum goong (2005) ialah filem Thai,Inggeris,Mandarin,Vietnam. Prachya Pinkaew telah mengarahkan filem ini. Tony Jaa,Nathan Jones,Xing Jin,Petchtai Wongkamlao adalah pelakon filem ini. Ia telah dikeluarkan pada tahun 2005. Tom yum goong (2005) dianggap sebagai salah satu filem Aksi, Jenayah, Drama, Thriller terbaik di India dan di seluruh dunia.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Bertahun-tahun selepas kematian ibunya, seorang wanita yang mengalami kerosakan emosi mencari bapanya yang hilang dan menghadapi masa lalunya.

programme.title: Vengeance Of An Assasin
programme.desc: The Assassins' Code - Berpegang teguh pada misi. Jangan sekali-kali mengalihkan pandangan anda dari sasaran. Tidak menunjukkan belas kasihan. Natee (Dan Chupong) menjadi pembunuh kerana satu sebab- untuk mengetahui siapa yang membunuh ibu bapanya. Apabila dia semakin hampir untuk mendedahkan rangkaian rahsia kuasa dan rasuah, dia melakukan dua kali ganda dalam kerja, menjadikannya sasaran dan meletakkan semua orang yang dia sayangi dalam bahaya. Dikhianati, didedahkan dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling maut dalam perniagaan, kini Natee mempunyai kod baharu. Jadi lebih pantas. Lebih kuat. Pukul lebih kuat. Bertahan.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep 5 Ep5
programme.desc: Kimi dan Tasya ikut Daniel serta Suhana melawat kubur Suzana. Tasya dirasuk semasa perjalanan balik dan menyanyikan lagu Tepukamai-amai tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Kimi, Daniel dan Suhana tidak percaya dengan Tasya. Hantu kanak-kanak tu datang mengganggu mereka pula.Menyanyikan lagu TepukAmai-amai di sudut bilik yang gelap.Akhirnya mereka cuba menyelesaikan masa

programme.title: The Secret Of Sinchanee
programme.desc: Seorang pemandu trak tunda industri yang mengalami insomnia kembali ke rumah zaman kanak-kanaknya selepas kematian bapanya, untuk mengetahui bahawa kehadiran paranormal telah tinggal di rumah itu dan menghantui tanah suci yang dibina di atasnya.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Kimi, Daniel dan Suhana tidak percaya dengan Tasya. Hantu kanak-kanak tu datang mengganggu mereka pula.Menyanyikan lagu TepukAmai-amai di sudut bilik yang gelap.Akhirnya mereka cuba menyelesaikan masa

programme.title: Takien
programme.desc: Semasa memburu haiwan, Wittaya dan Lokrai secara tidak sengaja menyinggung perasaan Nang Ta-Kian, roh penjaga hutan, yang kemudian membunuh Lokrai. Wittaya terpaksa menjaga anak kawannya, Tong Kam. Sebagai seorang lelaki muda, Tong Kam jatuh cinta dengan anak perempuan Wittaya, Porn tetapi Wittaya lebih suka Trai, seorang jurutera awam yang datang ke kampung mereka untuk menyelaraskan pembinaan empangan. Apabila empangan itu siap, kampung itu banjir dan Wittaya ditugaskan untuk membersihkan setiap pokok, termasuk pokok Ta-Kian yang besar

programme.title: 1BR
programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan seorang wanita yang baru berhijrah ke Los Angeles dan menetap di kompleks pangsapuri yang seolah-olah sempurna, dan tidak lama kemudian dia mendapati bahawa tanpa sedar dia telah mendapat dihukum akibat dari melanggar peraturan.

programme.title: Apartment
programme.desc: Sebuah apartmen di mana pembunuhan telah berlaku dihantui oleh beberapa siri kejadian paranormal dan tiada penyewa pernah tinggal lebih daripada 14 hari. Seorang novelis paranormal muda berpindah ke apartmen untuk menyiasat kes hantu wanita tanpa kepala dan mengalami beberapa peristiwa yang sangat menakutkan.

programme.title: Mercury Man
programme.desc: Selepas memberus dirinya dengan bahan pelik, rata-rata anggota bomba berubah menjadi sesuatu yang jauh lebih hebat daripada dirinya seperti Mercury Man. Dikurniakan kuasa besar yang hebat, dia kini akan menggunakan kebolehannya untuk membantu menakluki kuasa jahat.

programme.title: Sindiket
programme.desc: Diilhamkan daripada kisah benar, ia memaparkan sindiket pemerdagangan manusia dan menceritakan kisah seorang wanita yang ditipu oleh teman lelakinya. Dia telah dijual ke rumah pelacuran di mana dia dibius dan dipaksa untuk menjual dirinya.

programme.title: Arumi
programme.desc: 15 tahun selepas pembunuhan ibu dan abangnya, Rasty menjemput empat rakan ke vila ibu bapanya. Lawatan yang pada asalnya hanya untuk bercuti, berakhir jauh dari jangkaan mereka dengan pembunuhan yang menyusul semasa percutian itu.

programme.title: Sangkar
programme.desc: Adam dan Johan merupakan atlet sukan bela diri campuran (MMA). Adam bersikap angkuh dan telah menang sebuah pertarungan dengan taktik kotornya. Mereka ialah musuh dan selalu bersaing. Suatu hari, apabila dicabar di luar sangkar, Adam secara tidak sengaja mencederakan Johan. Johan tercedera parah dan ahli keluarganya hilang punca rezeki dan harapan. Untuk menebus kesalahannya, Adam kembali bertarung di pertarungan bawah tanah untuk mendapatkan habuan supaya dapat membantu Johan sekeluarga. Johan pula sedang bertarung dengan kesihatan dan pemulihan demi keluarganya. Pada saat ini, Adam mengingatkan tujuan diri sebagai pejuang MMA dan mengambil cabaran untuk berlawan dengan pejuang MMA antarabangsa.

programme.desc: Filler

programme.title: Bangkok Knock Out
programme.desc: Sekumpulan kawan "kelab pertarungan", yang gayanya berbeza dari Muay Thai, Capoeira hingga Kung Fu dan Tai Chi, mesti bergabung tenaga dan berjuang untuk nyawa mereka dalam menyelamatkan seorang rakan yang diculik.

programme.title: The Sacred Riana: Beginning
programme.desc: Pada zaman kanak-kanaknya, Riana tinggal di sebuah pekan kecil bersama ayah dan ibunya yang menjalankan perniagaan rumah pengebumian. Musibah yang datang memerlukan mereka berpindah ke rumah Pakcik Johan di Jakarta dan Riana bertemu dengan anak patung Riani. Riana semakin dewasa dan suatu hari telah dilawati oleh Puan Klara, seorang guru kaunselor di sekolahnya yang ingin mengetahui sebab Riana tidak hadir ke sekolah dan mencadangkan Riana untuk dipulihkan. Musibah menimpa ibu bapa Riana. Puan Klara datang lagi bersama Hendro, Lusi dan Anggi, untuk membantu Riana beramah mesra. Tetapi, kehadiran mereka mencetuskan masalah yang lebih besar.

programme.title: Khun Pan 2
programme.desc: Cerita ini mengisahkan tentang seorang pegawai polis bernama Khun Phan dalam Perang Dunia Kedua. Dia menjalankan misi penyamaran untuk menumpaskan seorang gabenor di sebuah pulau yang semua orang di sana dianggap penyamun.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Kimi, Daniel dan Suhana tidak percaya dengan Tasya. Hantu kanak-kanak tu datang mengganggu mereka pula.Menyanyikan lagu TepukAmai-amai di sudut bilik yang gelap.Akhirnya mereka cuba menyelesaikan masa

programme.title: Arjuna Ep26
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Paku
programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan tentang Fahmi (Johan As'ari) yang amat mencintai isterinya Riana (Aishah Ilias) dan dia tidak dapat menerima kenyataan bahawa isterinya sudah meninggal dunia. Oleh kerna disebabkan ketaksuban cintanya itu membuatkan Fahmi sanggup mencari seorang bomoh untuk menghidupkan semula Riana. Riana telah berjaya dihidupkan semula dan mereka bersatu sehinggalah Riana melahirkan seorang anak. Namun benarkah itu adalah Riana? Apakah yang akan terjadi kepada kehidupan Fahmi selepas itu?

programme.title: Cinta Metropolitan
programme.desc: Haris, seorang jurugambar bertemu semula dengan adiknya yang terkenal sebagai seorang casanova, Irwan. Tidak begitu senang dengan perangai adiknya yang suka menggoda sesiapa sahaja termasuk kekasihnya sendiri, hubungan mereka renggang. Satu sindiket pemalsuan wang terbongkar menyebabkan Haris, Irwan, Monisa dan dua orang lagi diburu sindiket itu sehingga ke luar negara.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona telah membawa diri dari Kelantan ke Kuala Lumpur kerana telah dimarahi oleh ayahnya akibat membuat sumbang di kampungnya. Di Kuala Lumpur, Mona menumpang tinggal bersama 6 orang gadis iaitu Esah, Afidah, Nina, Shamsiah, Ramlah dan Zakiah.Mona hanyut dengan kehidupan di kota. Dia banyak terpengaruh dengan kehidupan rakan-rakan serumahnya. Selepas tiga tahun Mona langsung tidak mengirim khabar pada ayahnya di kampung. Ayah Mona yang sedang sakit dan sangat merindui anaknya telah meminta bantuan anak muridnya Mail untuk mencari Mona di Kuala Lumpur.

programme.title: Api Cemburu
programme.desc: Akibat satu tragedi di mana Ratna diperkosa oleh seorang lelaki di hadapan suaminya, Johan, hubungan mereka menjadi semakin dingin. Lebih mengeruhkan keadaan, seminggu selepas peristiwa hitam itu Ratna didapati hamil. Johan berkeras agar kandungan itu digugurkan meskipun pandangan doktor mengatakan bahawa kandungan itu bukanlah berlaku daripada pemerkosaan itu. Tanpa disedari Ratna, apa yang berlaku kepada dirinya itu berpunca daripada dendam yang melibatkan hubungan sahabatnya, Maya dengan seorang lelaki.

programme.title: Sayang Ibu
programme.desc: Setelah kematian bapa akibat satu kebakaran, kehidupan Tiara dan ibunya menjadi semakin sulit. Mereka berdua kemudiannya menumpang tinggal di sebuah pondok. Tiara mempunyai suara yang merdu dan dia berjaya menjadi seorang penyanyi di sebuah Syarikat rakaman. Ketika berada di kota, Tiara meminta jasa baik teman lelakinya untuk menguruskan hal ehwal ibunya di kampung. Namun, teman lelakinya itu menyalahgunakan wang yang diberikan oleh Tiara untuk ibunya.

programme.title: SH3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang percintaan dan persaingan siapa yang terbaik antara pemain papan selaju ketika kemuncak musik Hip Hop dan sukan papan selaju di negara. Khairul, ingin menjadi pemain papan selaju yang terbaik tetapi menemui kesulitan kerana lawannya, Mario yang juga sama mahir. Ingin memenangi hati Nelly, Khairul ingin terus membuktikan kehandalannya. Pada masa yang sama, Mario dan Mawar berpakat bersama-sama untuk memastikan mereka mendapat Khairul dan Nelly untuk diri mereka sendiri. Sikap setiakawan dan keluarga menjadi penyokong kuat Khairul untuk berjaya.

programme.title: Antara Dua Hati
programme.desc: Perkenalan antara Sharifah dan Jefri telah sedikit sebanyak membuka pintu hatinya untuk mencari pengganti arwah suaminya. Tetapi dalam masa yang sama, Jefri pula berkenalan rapat dengan Ina, anak perempuan kepada Sharifah tanpa pengetahuan Sharifah. Manakala Shah pula menyokong ibunya untuk berkahwin buat kali kedua agar kehidupan ibunya berubah dan tidak berasa sunyi lagi. Ina pula sanggup mengetepikan kekasih lamanya, Joe yang menaruh hati terhadapnya sejak dari dulu lagi kerana sudah terpikat dengan Jefri namun Jefri telah pun menaruh hati pada Sharifah.

programme.title: Cinta 200 Ela
programme.desc: Mengisahkan persahabatan Yazid dan Yati yang bekerja sebagai caddy di sebuah kelab golf. Yazid menanam impian untuk menjadi seorang pemain golf terkenal suatu hari nanti. Tanpa disedari, Yati menyimpan perasaan cinta kepada Yazid. Pada suatu hari, kelab golf tempat mereka bekerja dikunjungi oleh seorang Dato Mustafa bersama anaknya, Nor. Yazid mendapat peluang untuk bermain golf yang dimiliki oleh Dato Mustafa di Kuala Lumpur dan dia berjaya membawa kejayaan kepada kelab itu. Tidak lama kemudian, Yazid menjadi semakin rapat dengan Nor sehingga perkara itu mengguris perasaan Yati.

programme.title: Riang Tirana
programme.desc: Sham menyamar sebagai seorang perempuan untuk meletakkan hadiah di bilik Tirana setelah diminta oleh Zaihan. Tetapi hadiah tersebut dipulangkan kembali oleh Tirana kerana ingin menjaga persahabatan antaranya dan Ikram. Zaihan, seorang pelajar cemerlang dan anak orang berada suka mengusik Tirana dan mencabar Ikram. Persengketaan angkara cinta tiga segi mula berlaku antara mereka.

programme.title: Jiwa Remaja
programme.desc: Hairi bekerja sebagai jurugambar di sebuah syarikat. Dia kemudiannya diberhentikan kerja kerana ingkar pada arahan majikannya. Dengan bantuan sahabatnya Joey, Hairi mendapat pekerjaan di sebuah hotel. Hairi berkenalan dengan Anita, anak seorang hartawan dan jatuh cinta dengannya. Yusof, abang kepada Anita tidak menyukai Hairi kerana perbezaan darjat. Apabila berlaku satu kejadian yang menyebabkan kematian Joey, Hairi bertekad untuk membalas dendam terhadap Yusof.

programme.title: Sepet
programme.desc: Sepasang kekasih melalui pelbagai halangan dalam percintaan kerana keduanya berasal dari latar belakang yang berbeza. Orked mencintai Jason yang berbangsa Cina dan bukan beragama Islam. Disebabkan itu pelbagai tekanan terpaksa mereka hadapi kerana stereotaip bangsa dan berlainan agama namun berjaya mereka hadapinya bersama-sama.

programme.title: Ke Medan Jaya
programme.desc: Hisham tinggal bersama ibunya, Mak Jah. Bapanya yang bekerja sebagai anggota tentera telah meninggal dunia akibat serangan musuh semasa zaman darurat. Sejak kematian suaminya, Mak Jah bekerja sebagai pembantu rumah dengan seorang hartawan bernama Pak Samad. Pak Samad dan isterinya tidak pernah menganggap Mak Jah sebagai pembantu rumah, malah Hisham dianggap seperti anak mereka sendiri dan mendapat pendidikan yang sama dengan Haryati, anak hartawan tersebut. Apabila wujud kemesraan antara mereka berdua, ibu bapa Haryati merasa bimbang kerana Haryati telah ditunangkan dengan Shahril. Setelah mengetahui kisah sebenar, Hisham mengambil Keputusan untuk menyertai angkatan tentera walaupun ditentang oleh ibunya.

programme.title: Layar Lara
programme.desc: Ena Manjalara ialah seorang pelakon berbakat yang mengidolakan Seniwati Zai, seorang pelakon handalan pada tahun 1950-an. Namun, Ena mempunyai masalah disiplin dan sering menimbulkan pelbagai masalah di lokasi penggambaran. Dia terperangkap dalam keghairahan mengejar cinta dan kerjaya. Ena telah memperalatkan Daud, seorang pembantu produksi merangkap pelakon tambahan sehingga ia mencetuskan konflik dalam produksi tersebut. Akibat daripada itu, Ena telah dibuang daripada penggambaran filem.

Dia banyak terpengaruh dengan kehidupan rakan-rakan serumahnya. Selepas tiga tahun Mona langsung tidak mengirim khabar pada ayahnya di kampung. Ayah Mona yang sedang sakit dan sangat merindui anaknya telah meminta bantuan anak muridnya Mail untuk mencari Mona di Kuala Lumpur.

programme.title: SH3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang percintaan dan persaingan siapa yang terbaik antara pemain papan selaju ketika kemuncak musik Hip Hop dan sukan papan selaju di negara. Khairul, ingin menjadi pemain papan selaju yang terbaik tetapi menemui kesulitan kerana lawannya, Mario yang juga sama mahir. Ingin memenangi hati Nelly, Khairul ingin terus membuktikan kehandalannya. Pada masa yang sama, Mario dan Mawar berpakat bersama-sama untuk memastikan mereka mendapat Khairul dan Nelly untuk diri mereka sendiri. Sikap setiakawan dan keluarga menjadi penyokong kuat Khairul untuk berjaya.

programme.title: Sepet
programme.desc: Sepasang kekasih melalui pelbagai halangan dalam percintaan kerana keduanya berasal dari latar belakang yang berbeza. Orked mencintai Jason yang berbangsa Cina dan bukan beragama Islam. Disebabkan itu pelbagai tekanan terpaksa mereka hadapi kerana stereotaip bangsa dan berlainan agama namun berjaya mereka hadapinya bersama-sama.

programme.title: Cinta 200 Ela
programme.desc: Mengisahkan persahabatan Yazid dan Yati yang bekerja sebagai caddy di sebuah kelab golf. Yazid menanam impian untuk menjadi seorang pemain golf terkenal suatu hari nanti. Tanpa disedari, Yati menyimpan perasaan cinta kepada Yazid. Pada suatu hari, kelab golf tempat mereka bekerja dikunjungi oleh seorang Dato Mustafa bersama anaknya, Nor. Yazid mendapat peluang untuk bermain golf yang dimiliki oleh Dato Mustafa di Kuala Lumpur dan dia berjaya membawa kejayaan kepada kelab itu. Tidak lama kemudian, Yazid menjadi semakin rapat dengan Nor sehingga perkara itu mengguris perasaan Yati.

programme.title: Riang Tirana
programme.desc: Sham menyamar sebagai seorang perempuan untuk meletakkan hadiah di bilik Tirana setelah diminta oleh Zaihan. Tetapi hadiah tersebut dipulangkan kembali oleh Tirana kerana ingin menjaga persahabatan antaranya dan Ikram. Zaihan, seorang pelajar cemerlang dan anak orang berada suka mengusik Tirana dan mencabar Ikram. Persengketaan angkara cinta tiga segi mula berlaku antara mereka.

programme.title: Cinta Metropolitan
programme.desc: Haris, seorang jurugambar bertemu semula dengan adiknya yang terkenal sebagai seorang casanova, Irwan. Tidak begitu senang dengan perangai adiknya yang suka menggoda sesiapa sahaja termasuk kekasihnya sendiri, hubungan mereka renggang. Satu sindiket pemalsuan wang terbongkar menyebabkan Haris, Irwan, Monisa dan dua orang lagi diburu sindiket itu sehingga ke luar negara.

programme.title: Sayang Ibu
programme.desc: Setelah kematian bapa akibat satu kebakaran, kehidupan Tiara dan ibunya menjadi semakin sulit. Mereka berdua kemudiannya menumpang tinggal di sebuah pondok. Tiara mempunyai suara yang merdu dan dia berjaya menjadi seorang penyanyi di sebuah Syarikat rakaman. Ketika berada di kota, Tiara meminta jasa baik teman lelakinya untuk menguruskan hal ehwal ibunya di kampung. Namun, teman lelakinya itu menyalahgunakan wang yang diberikan oleh Tiara untuk ibunya.

There are two main themes for the program, which are Big Stars Come to Cook and Five-Star Cooking Show. <Stylish Man The Chef> containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep41604806
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep193
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: In the Family (T) Ep371372
programme.desc: "Home" as axis X and "love" as axis Y, this piece exquisitely depicts the ups and downs in life of an ordinary family. From touching sibling love, to the struggles and entanglement of parent-child relationship, the show elaborates on the importance of encountering the surroundings with a positive attitude. Through a bowl of beef noodle soup, Hui-wen and Chien-chin teach their four daughters, Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter, how to behave around others. The heartwarming play is relaxing, fun, humorous, and a tearjerker.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep110
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep259260
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep484
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Home Sweet Home (M) Ep2021
programme.desc: Every one of them showed up in this house with some sort of lacking until they've met Mommy Hsiao-Li. Although they are not biologicap related, they Stay with each other like a real family.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: Born to Fly
programme.desc: Lei Yu has officially become the new generation of Chinese test pilots after rounds of strict selection. Captain Zhang Ting leads Lei Yu and other pilots to test the latest fighter jets. Lei Yu keeps pushing the limits in each test flight in the hope of coming up with the perfect plane to ensure the safety of the fighter pilots.

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Deception of the Novelist
programme.desc: This is a sexy thriller adapted from the hit story by the famous internet author, Xxharuki. A self-help book author Xu lives happily with his wife Jeana and their son. However, when a voluptuous and seductive tenant rents their apartment upstairs, Xus life is turned upside down.

programme.title: Love For All Seasons
programme.desc: May, acting leader of the Er Mei sect, cures the incurable illness of Tiger, a rich playboy. Under the threat of her senior, May seeks help from Tiger to experience heartbreak and master the "Heartbroken Sword" style, so as to defeat her senior and preserve Er Mei sect. Will this strange and long-winding relationship reach a happy ending?

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Fight Back to School
programme.desc: The number one killer in SDU, Chow Sing Sing(Stephen Chow), is sent to a school to find a lost gun. His partner Tat(Ng Man Tat) pretends to be a school worker in assisting him. They recognize that some students are being closed with Fei, the head of triad society, and Fei traffics munitions. Sing steals and ignites Fei's munitions; Fei pledges to kill Sing...

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughters diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: Golden Chicken 2
programme.desc: The sequel is set in 2046 when a 82-year-old Ah Kam stops a heartbroken young man from taking memory loss pills. To help ease his pain, Ah Kam shares her life stories from 2003, one of Hong Kongs toughest year with SARS, including the different people she comes across and the bittersweet romance between herself and her cousin.

programme.title: Death Notice
programme.desc: A serial killer leaves death notices in a city, stating when, how and who he will murder. Even if the victims report it to the police and receive protection, the killer can still break through and execute them. While the police sets up a special task force in response, they expose an even bigger conspiracy behind.

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: Ah Boys to Men
programme.desc: Ken is a rich and spoiled young man reluctant to be enlisted into National Service but must do so by law. He has to endure harsh training but it is made more bearable when he befriends three other recruits. When his girlfriend breaks up with him, Ken tries all ways to escape from camp so as to chase her back, but this leads to dire consequences

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Love on Delivery
programme.desc: A delivery boy Yin wants to impress his dream girl Li, so he enrols in a martial arts course to learn strange moves. Being timid, Yin saves Li while wearing a Garfield mask but the credit is stolen by Karate Master, Liu. To prove himself and win Li back, Yin defeats Liu in the ring with his unique martial arts move "Invincible Wind and Fire Spin".

programme.title: Don't Forget I Love You
programme.desc: Lu Yao suffers from amnesia and forgets about everything that happens yesterday when he wakes up the next day. When Lu Yao meets psychotherapist Xing Yue, they fall in love despite knowing they have no future together, and are determined to love each other no matter what happens...

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: God of Gambler's Return
programme.desc: The God of Gamblers, Gao Jin, quits gambling and live a quiet life with his wife. However, a Taiwanese crime boss wants to become the new God of Gamblers and get rid of him, so he kills Gao Jins pregnant wife to force him to the casino table. Gao Jin is indignant and vows to fight the crime boss to avenge his wifes death.

programme.title: Shadows
programme.desc: Ching is a forensic psychiatrist who has the power to enter a persons subconscious mind. In her latest case, she suspects that another psychiatrist is responsible for a brutal murder-cum-suicide case involving a social worker. In the investigation process, Ching finds herself under suspicion instead, as she comes face-to-face with a past trauma

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Changs first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunts puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: My Name Ain't Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: Murder Plot
programme.desc: Martial artist Shen Lang is in discussions with kung fu experts from the other six sects to plot the downfall of the traitorous Happy King when his fiance suddenly disrupts them and Shen has to quickly bring her away. As they continue to pursue the Happy King, both Shen and his fiance accidentally fall into a trap set up by the King.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: Killer Darts
programme.desc: A group of bandits raided the village where dart master Liu lives and killed his wife. While hunting them down, Lius disciple kills a farmer and his wife when she refuses his advances, leading Liu to adopt their orphaned daughter and raises her with his son. Years later, the daughter meets a man with the bandits and is tricked to go against Liu.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Oath Of Death
programme.desc: Three Sung loyalists become blood brothers to fight the tyranny of the Tartar invaders. To oust the oppressors altogether, Ma releases the kidnapped Tartar princess in a strategic effort to gain points with the invaders, but it soon becomes apparent that he desires both a great position and power, and will do anything to get it

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friends grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: Hell Has No Boundary
programme.desc: Cheng Chung (Derek Yee) and May (Liu Hsueh-hua), a pair of lovers working on the police force, camp on an outlying island. Awakened by a strange sound, May goes out onto the beach where a violent frenzy grips her. After her return from leave, May insists Inspector Wang (Yueh Hua) in a bid to rescue some hostages. She shoots the thug under most peculiar circumstances. Then a series of tragedies occur. Her two colleagues die mangled in a lift accident and Inspector Wang is injured at his desk by a snake. Wang's exorcist sister (Hsia Ping), who performs rites for him, also dies in an accident. And so does a fortune-teller who refused to read May's fortune.

programme.title: Pursuit of Vengeance
programme.desc: Kung Fu legend Ti Lung stars in the action movie as Fu Xue Hong, embarking on a epic journey of revenge for his father.

programme.title: The Lady Assassin
programme.desc: Two feuding princes fight for the throne in the Qing Dynasty, causing many injuries and deaths to the commoners. Can the lady assassin who is drawn into this royal feud execute her assassination mission in time to help one of the princes secure the throne?

programme.title: The Female Prince
programme.desc: Hsiao's stepmother frames her fianc Lung when he refuses to forfeit their engagement and sends him to prison. To save him, Hsiao disguises as Lung to take the Imperial exam and ranks first place. Impressed by Hsiao, the Emperor weds the Princess to 'him'. When Hsiao comes clean on their wedding night, she persuades the Princess to follow a plan

programme.title: Pursuit of a Killer
programme.desc: The charm of Pursuit Of A Killer lies in the long awaited reunion of Five Venoms duo, Lo Meng and Sun Chien; Lo Meng, who plays a Mainland Chinese criminal escapee to Hong Kong in search of a better life, and a cop (Sun Chien) who helps him adjust to Hong Kong life while tracking down his mysterious killer at the same time.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: The Eunuch
programme.desc: A year before Lo Wei directed Bruce Lee in Fist Of Fury, he wrote and co-starred in this tale of a treacherous devil who wants nothing less than supreme power...and doesn't care if he has to murder the Emperor and use his own daughter as a deadly dupe to get it.

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: Rolls, Rolls, I Love You
programme.desc: Three young men offend a billionaire and are drawn into a high stakes bet. If they win, they get to keep the billionaires Rolls Royce. Otherwise, they will need to pay the rich man fifty thousand dollars! Will the underdogs win the bet?

programme.title: Return of the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A kung fu anthology film consisting of three stories: a man embarrasses himself while trying to prove his worth to the father of the woman he loves; a courtesan in love with a general will need to deliver a notorious bandit in exchange for him not being executed; and a group of bandits forms a plan to rescue a new friend from being executed.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insiders look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiangs popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: Six Assassins
programme.desc: Lord Li Ming is a feudal tyrant who oppresses the people, and even the Emperor who is his brother, cannot stop his evil act. Righteous swordsman Mu poses as Li Mings guard to plan for his assassination. He arrests six assassins who have tried to kill Li Ming, before making them his allies in a secret plot to kill him and end the tyranny.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: 7-Man Army
programme.desc: This iconoclastic film retells the legend of seven Chinese patriots, who sacrificed their lives to defend against 20,000 Japanese soldiers and 50 tanks for 5 days, at a strategic key point of the Great Wall known as Pa Tou Lou Tzu.

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Long Road to Gallantry
programme.desc: Tu Meng Fei makes his way to the world after completing his kung fu training. En route, he rescues Mu Wan Erh and Li San Nan from a band of thugs and later learnt of a 20-year conflict between the evil Thunder Gang Chief Leng Tian Lei and the Dragon Sect. Mus lost father is none other than the Thunder Gang Chief, who also killed Lis father

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the generals escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate, beset by enemies and sinister Japanese interference along the way.

programme.title: The Love Eterne
programme.desc: Ying Tai disguises herself as a boy to go to school and falls hopelessly in love with her classmate, Shan Bo. After Shan Bo realizes her true identity, he proposes marriage to Ying Tai. However, they are kept apart as she is engaged to another man. Knowing Shan Bo died in despair, Ying Tai is in deep sorrow and kills herself at his grave.

programme.title: The Singing Killer
programme.desc: Chiang Yi is blackmailed into a jewelry heist by his former boss, who threatens to expose his shady past. Complications arise when he discovers his first love works at the store.

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Tang Peng Nan are a sweet couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan at a time when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he found that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: Mysteries of Evolution 1 Ep5
programme.desc: Social Animals - Cooperation comes in many forms. Some animals cooperate to be social while others put the welfare of the group above their own reproductive potential. See the many ways species have evolved to work with one another in order to survive.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Growing Up Gibbon - Hoolock Gibbons are true specialists of the Indian Jungle. Living in close knit family groups, youngsters must spend up to 9 years learning all the skills required to survive alone. From finding food in unusual places, to avoiding dangerous predators and mastering the acrobatics required for a life in the trees, we follow Samar as he finally comes of age and takes his first step into the wild.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Land of the Secret Rhino - The grasslands of Northeast India are one of the most fertile habitats on earth. Hundreds of species of tall grass flourish here, allowing one of Indias most iconic creatures to thrive the Greater One-horned Rhino. This is one of the last places on earth where this gentle giant survives. Rani, an adult female has just had a baby, Rajah. This young rhino calf is only 3-month-old and his mom is his teacher, for the first year and half of his life. Rajah has much to learn, as he gets to grips with the world around him and everything there is to know about being a rhino.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep3
programme.desc: Wild Stallions of the Himalayas - The high altitude Ladakh plateau in northwest India is a land of extremes. The air is thin and the mountain landscape treacherous; winters are freezing, while summers are scorching hot. The Tibetan wild ass is king of these grasslands, and one old stallion has developed a way to stay one step ahead of his rivals. We follow Dorje as he shadows a herd of females and foals, from winter to summer, when he will get his chance to sire the next generation. But to win his prize he must eventually do battle with other stallions - all wanting his crown!

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep4
programme.desc: A Sloth Bear's Dilemma - In a land of searing summer heat and thunderous tropical storms, life for all that live on the plains of southern India is tough. But this year its harder than ever as the monsoon rains are late to arrive. For Bibi, a female sloth bear with two young cubs, this will be the biggest challenge of her life. With no rainfall, food will be hard to find and her cubs are also open to attack from leopards and other bears. Bibi must guide her family through this tricky time. Does she have the experience for them all to survive?

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep26
programme.desc: The Case Of Smartysaurus's Rainbow Experiment - Noddy's back on the case when something goes wrong with Smartysaurus's rainbow experiment . He needs to investigate. He figures out that the rainbow colours have all been put in a different order. Using his investigation kit and all his who, what, why, where, when and how questions he e follows all the clues - which leads him eventually to Fuse's workshop. Fuse admits that he changed the order of the rainbow test tubes from colour to size order. He's very sorry for ruining the experiment! Noddy helps Smartysaurus reorder the colours and this time the Rainbow experiment is a huge success! Case closed!

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep26
programme.desc: Why Woodpecker Pecks - You see there was a time when Woodpecker didn't peck. All the birds had their very own sound, but Woodpecker didn't make a sound at all. Then one very dark night in Tinga Tinga, the Moon and the Stars disappear! The animals summon the birds to tell Lion but Woodpecker can't pass the message on! Distraught, Woodpecker flies up to the skies but where are the stars?! And where is the Moon?! In desperation Woodpecker pecks at the dark sky and a star comes back, then another, then another! Everyone is delighted, no beast more than Woodpecker who now has her very own special sound pecking.

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep26
programme.desc: Putting On A Show - The cars are all gleaming for this evening's race. Roary gets bored and heads out onto the track - with disastrous consequences. Will the cars be ready in time for the big show?

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep26
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Very Important Person - PC Selby is being honoured with a medal for being Best local Policeman of the year and Pat is despatched to Pencaster bay to collect both the medal and the person who is going to present it; The Duchess of Pencaster! Somewhat star struck Pat and Jess drive the Duchess towards Pencaster back to the award ceremony at Greendale but at her request they stop to help some of the villagers which unfortunately leads to her getting covered in coal dust and mud! PC Selby is also on his way to Greendale and also finds people in need of help and his best uniform is soon torn and covered in paint and compost! The Duchess and PC Selby meet and wonder quite how they are going to explain their tattered appearance to the crowd at the award ceremony. Luckily Pat explains how both PC Selby and The Duchess put helping others before themselves. Special delivery service mission accomplished!

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep1
programme.desc: The Nest - When the Rescue Riders save Viking chief Duggard, theyre invited to visit his village of Huttsgalor, where they must prove they're kind and helpful.

programme.title: Dinotrux Ep1
programme.desc: Ty And Revvit - Meet Ty Rux and his buddy Revvit as they join forces with the giant Dinotrux team that are half dinosaur, half construction truck and full-on fun!

programme.desc: Crazy Fast - Turbo must become a hero by saving the city from a menacing tiger beetle, who has challenged him to a race on an insane stunt-filled obstacle course.

programme.desc: The Neighs Have It - The PALs run into their old rivals the BUDs on the first day of classes, prompting Lucky to run for class rep. Elsewhere, Abigail helps solve a mystery.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep14
programme.desc: Raiders of the Lost Bark / Slow, Dog. Slow! - When Tag and Scooch break Gilbers ancient Golden Slipper, they embark on an adventure to a secret cave to retrieve the matching slipper. \ For community outreach day, the Race Cadets are paired with an elderly resident of Pawston. It's Tag and Scooch's job to take old dog Leo around town for a day of slow, relaxing activities. But when Leo wants to kickbarx, row and skydive, Tag and Scooch try their best to keep up.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep27
programme.desc: The Case Of The Lost Race - Noddy is suspicious when Revs suddenly slows down during a race on the roller coaster in DareDale. He doesn't like to lose and doesn't understand what's happened. Noddy needs to investigate so that they don't lose another race! Using all his investigate skills Noddy follows the clues to the Farm where he finds out that Revs deliberately slowed down so his friend Tractor wouldn't come last as usual. Noddy realises what a great friend Revs is to Tractor. He suggests that they have another race for fun and not just to win. This time EVERYONE has fun! Well done Noddy!

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep27
programme.desc: Why Ostrich Sticks Her Head In The Ground - You see there was a time when Ostrich was all covered in feathers and unlike all the other birds, Ostrich wasn't very good at flying at all. One night in Tinga Tinga Spider decided to make Jackal a pair of wings so that he could fly up to the moon and stop howling! Jackal and Spider stole the feathers from Ostrich's neck and legs until she looked like a very big plucked chicken! The next day Ostrich was mortified and stuck her head in the ground so that Lion couldn't see her. And it was perfect because Ostrich looked just like a bush! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep27
programme.desc: Motor Mouth - The track inspector is coming to visit and Big Chris is too tired to commentate on the race. A celebrity commentator is brought in to save the day - much to Big Chris' anger.

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep1
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Cornish Caper - Ted Glenn's Cornish cousin Ned is sending him a steam engine as an alternative means to power his workshop. Pat and Jess set off to Cornwall to collect this very large special delivery in the SDS Plane whilst Ted sets about giving away all of his old inventions to the people of Greendale in order to clear out enough space for the engine. Pat and Jess meet the eccentric Ned Glenn at his workshop and wrestle with the crate containing the heavy engine to get it aboard the plane. Back in Greendale the villagers are only too delighted to take all of Ted's weird and wonderful inventions off his hands but the more inventions that go, the more gloomy Ted gets. After a trip over a very bumpy field and flight in the plane, Pat finally delivers the engine to a now very sad Ted. He's depressed because he loves to tinkering with things, and now he has nothing left to tinker with. Maybe the engine will cheer him up but when Pat takes the side off the crate, just a heap of engine parts spill out. The engine was shaken apart on the journey. Pat is very sorry but Ted is delighted. Now he has something to tinker with again! Mission accomplished!

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep28
programme.desc: The Case Of The Broken Xylophone Bridge - Everyone is enjoying playing games on Toy Green but when Noddy and Big Ears come back from apple picking at the farm they discover someone, or something, has broken a key on the xylophone bridge. Noddy needs to investigate! With the help of Bumpy and Revs and using the wwwbook to gather clues, Noddy discovers that someone has tried to fix it with purple sticky tape. If he can find out who uses purple sticky tape he might discover who broke the key. The trail leads him to Smartysaurus, who broke the bridge by mistake when she was playing bowling. Noddy and Deltoid show the big dinosaur how to play the game without breaking anything else. Good job, Noddy!

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep28
programme.desc: Why Camel Has A Hump - You see there was time when Camel didn't have a hump. He lived very far away in the hot desert. But one day the desert got too hot even for Camel. So he started walking. When Camel arrived at the Waterhole he asked the animals if he good have a drink. All the animals weren't pleased at all because the rains hadn't come and they were very thirsty. Lion allowed Camel to have one drink but ONE drink, and ONE DRINK ONLY! Camel slurped, and he slurped, and he slurped! Until POP!' a big, wobbly hump appeared on his back full of all the animals' water! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep28
programme.desc: Dancing Queen - Christine is due to take part in a dancing competition and is practising at Silver Hatch. But what happens when her dance partner is taken ill?

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep2
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Giant Pumpkin - Pat has to deliver some pumpkins to Greendale School for the annual Halloween Pumpkin Party. But when he picks them up from Ted's workshop, Jess starts playing with a giant pumpkin and it rolls into the river and floats away. Pat follows it along the river and tries to fish it out with Alf's rod but the pumpkin is too heavy and the line breaks. As the party gets under way in Greendale, the giant pumpkin floats out to sea and Pat and Jess board the SDS Orca and head out into Pencaster Bay. With help from Chris Beacon and his radar machine they at last manage to locate the pumpkin then hurry back to Greendale just in time. Pat then surprises everyone by arriving with the giant pumpkin now carved with a big Jess face!
